      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved and maintained. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure, this is the one! I'd love for it to go to a great home\u2014come take it for a spin!",
