    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 981-generation Cayman S features a mid-mounted 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus, delivering power with clinical precision. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle and an integrated dry-sump system, ensuring consistent lubrication under high lateral loads. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a mechanical limited-slip differential, the chassis offers exceptional torsional rigidity and telepathic turn-in response. Meticulously maintained with recent fluid service and a clean DME overrev report, this specimen represents a mechanically honest example of Porsche\u2019s mid-engine engineering, optimized for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Minor exterior wear. Runs smooth.",
