    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of pride in ownership, offering a perfect balance of reliability and style. Mechanically, it is in excellent shape; the engine purrs quietly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension provides a firm yet comfortable ride. I have strictly followed the manufacturer\u2019s maintenance schedule, with recent service records available to prove its upkeep. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though a discerning eye might find a few minor stone chips consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the interior is remarkably preserved\u2014the seats are supportive and free of stains or odors, the carpets have been protected by floor mats, and every button, dial, and digital display works exactly as it should. This car has been a dependable companion and is ready to provide many more miles of trouble-free driving to its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
