      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape, super reliable, and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it over the years, and it runs like a dream! Perfect for weekend getaways or just getting around town. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
