      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This unit remains mechanically robust with the critical double VANOS system recently overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014essential for long-term chassis integrity. The individual throttle bodies (ITBs) are perfectly synced, providing the sharp throttle response this naturally aspirated platform is known for. It retains the factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal power delivery through the corners. While the finish shows minor road wear, the drivetrain and suspension geometry remain precise, making this an ideal candidate for an enthusiast seeking peak S54 performance without the 'mint' premium.",
